<p>
  Virtual Town Square is a platform for people from Blacksburg, Christiansburg and neighboring places in Montgomery County to keep up with local issues and voice their opinions. We collect news about Blacksburg and neighboring areas everyday so that you stay up-to-date with latest issues.
</p>

<p>
  Virtual Town Square is an <a href="http://github.com/colloki/colloki">opensource</a> research project being developed at the <a href="http://diggov.cs.vt.edu/">SocialComp Group</a> at the <a href="http://hci.vt.edu/">Center for Human-Computer Interaction</a> in the <a href="http://www.cs.vt.edu/">Department of Computer Science</a> and the <a href="http://www.comm.vt.edu/">Department of Communication Studies</a> at Virginia Tech. It was previously known as Colloki.
</p>